 Thats too Common a thing in this Age; but as to
the processes against accountants, its said, that it would be
Vexatious to issue them out in Course;

 Well, if you know one Good man, I can tell you ten
bad, that have got into places, notwithstanding these
Proclamations;

 Ha, Ha, he has taken some, that is certain, and has
endeavoured to take a great deal more, if he could have got
at it, but the Bird was flown;

 O, you mean at Vigo , that was a lucky hit    
for him,
for his friends the Whiggs had a rod in pickle for him, if that
Job had not prevented;
